## How to contribute

**Inline tagging** (the easiest path): in any `‹role›/‹project›/memory/PROJECT.md`, write tags like:

```
[LESSON]: something that worked well — be specific, one line
[PATTERN]: reusable approach we discovered here
[GOTCHA]: subtle thing that bit us — include the fix
[TOOL]: library / CLI / service that's genuinely useful — include why
```

The **Stop hook** scrapes these automatically after each session and appends them to `{{ROLE_NAME}}/memory/_pending.md`.

**Promoting to this ROLE.md**: run `/role-promote {{ROLE_NAME}}` to auto-reconcile (a sonnet subagent reads all pending content, dedupes, declutters, integrates). This fires automatically when the brain is >7 days stale with pending activity.

**Capturing before promoting**: run `/capture {{ROLE_NAME}}` to scrape tagged insights from changed files into `_pending.md`, then `/role-promote {{ROLE_NAME}}` to reconcile them into here.
